com.jidesoft.diff
Class Diff<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.jidesoft.diff.Diff<T>

public class Diff<T>
extends Object

Compares two lists, returning a list of the additions, changes, and deletions between them. A Comparator may be passed as an argument to the constructor, and will thus be used. If not provided, the initial value in the a ("from") list will be looked at to see if it supports the Comparable interface. If so, its equals and compareTo methods will be invoked on the instances in the "from" and "to" lists; otherwise, for speed, hash codes from the objects will be used instead for comparison.
